---
import FadeIn from '../FadeIn';
---
<section id="about" class="section py-20 md:py-32" style="background: rgb(var(--color-bg-primary));">
  <FadeIn client:visible>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-4xl md:text-6xl text-center font-bold" style="color: rgb(var(--color-text-primary));">About Me</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <!-- Image -->
        <div class="md:w-2/5">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/me.svg" 
              alt="France Laurence Velarde" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div class="md:w-3/5 space-y-6 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-justify" style="color: rgb(var(--color-text-primary));">
          <p>
            Hey! I’m France Laurence Velarde, a third-year BSIT student and Full Stack Developer based in Cebu, Philippines. I specialize in building projects end-to-end, taking full ownership of the entire lifecycle—from planning system architecture and designing databases to developing clean, scalable frontends and backends.
          </p>
          <p>
            Creativity drives my approach to tech. Beyond writing code, I focus heavily on design systems, UX interactions, and product design to ensure my applications are intuitive and meaningful. I also bring concepts to life through graphic and logo design, translating ideas into clear visual communication.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether I'm developing a complex system, designing a user interface, or creating engaging video content, my goal remains the same: to combine solid system architecture, thoughtful design, and creative execution to build products that make a real impact.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </FadeIn>
</section>
